name: politico
text:
Joe Kennedy's candidacy was designed around the idea that a vote for him was an investment in his seemingly limitless political future, while Ed Markey was already on his way out the door

https://t.co/eyGLlZQi8J

name: politico
text:
What Kennedy didn't envision was the way Markey would reinvent himself as a darling of the progressive left over the course of the year, harnessing the energy of young voters and climate activists

https://t.co/eyGLlZQi8J
